{
  "stem": "1363.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they all had to come with me to the, the marching.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And what they had done, we have marched first day, 25 kilometers to the brick factory of Obuda.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's a very well-known place by now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because those people in Budapest, whoever were leftover, they all, every day, 2,500 had to gather together, and go to the brick factory, spend the night there under dreadful circumstances.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And next day they gathered together the people, whoever survived it--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jews who were gathered together on that sports ground.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we, we walked again 25 kilometers to the next station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that went on for five days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For every five days, we went 25 kilometers walking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, don't forget, by that time all those women, 90%-- there were hardly any men-- they were some sort of invalids in one way or other, men who were left behind.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because all of the others were already in force camp, labor camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was one incident I want to mention in the brick factory, where one of the women-- I was sitting, laying down with my aunties, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] trying to discuss how are we going to try to run away or get away from that certain situation.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When all of a sudden-- yeah-- and we, as the women in our family, had wedding ring or had a little [NON-ENGLISH] on the neck, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, we were trying to hide it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now what they've said, being sort of a young girl, they said they won't do anything to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they put all the jewelry into my turban.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because the turban looked like a scarf, which you twist around and then you put it into a roll.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
